				<div id="post-664" class="post-664 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-as3 category-parallax-and-tiles category-platform-game category-technical tag-adobe-flash tag-game-developement tag-platform-game-2 tag-platformer tag-tiles">
					<h1 class="entry-title">How to make a 2d Platform Game &#8211; part 1</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/2011/12/11/how-to-make-a-2d-platform-game-part-1/" title="4:06 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">December 11, 2011</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/author/paulfirth/" title="View all posts by Paul Firth">Paul Firth</a></span>					</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<img width="150" height="142" src="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/giantStar-150x142.png" class="attachment-single-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="giantStar" />						
				<!-- Social Sharing Toolkit v2.0.4 | http://www.marijnrongen.com/wordpress-plugins/social_sharing_toolkit/ -->
				<div class="mr_social_sharing_wrapper"><span class="mr_social_sharing"><script type="text/javascript">
